een fortunate to be able to do that and bring it all the way to 3\\u00c3\\u00973, where it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s been an incredible ride.\", \"from\": 752, \"to\": 868, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"3\\u00c3\\u00973\", \"from\": 825, \"to\": 829}, {\"ngram\": \"it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 837, \"to\": 843}, {\"ngram\": \"an incredible ride\", \"from\": 849, \"to\": 867}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ve been able to leave an imprint on the game of basketball, and my legacy\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s been solidified,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Fredette reflected in arecent interview.\", \"from\": 869, \"to\": 1019, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an imprint\", \"from\": 903, \"to\": 913}, {\"ngram\": \"the game\", \"from\": 917, \"to\": 925}, {\"ngram\": \"basketball\", \"from\": 929, \"to\": 939}, {\"ngram\": \"my legacy\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 945, \"to\": 958}, {\"ngram\": \"Fredette\", \"from\": 979, \"to\": 987}, {\"ngram\": \"arecent interview\", \"from\": 1001, \"to\": 1018}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Unable to land a permanent spot in the NBA, Fredette found success overseas, winning a Greek Basket League championship and earning MVP honors in the Chinese Basketball Association with the Shanghai Sharks.\", \"from\": 1021, \"to\": 1227, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1060, \"end\": 1063, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.0907567788607782e-20, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 1065, \"end\": 1073, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmer_Fredette\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Fredette\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmer_Fredette\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/